      <item>
        <title>Polyphonic pitch bend</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[Auxy]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>There are probably “better” ways to edit pitch bends in the note editor, compared to using automation. Although we added the automation feature because it was an easy win when we added automation in general. Adding pitch to the editor would require a lot of work and it’s not the highest priority at the moment. We have some more exciting things coming up now that we cover pitch with automation.</p>
<p>I also think that polyphonic pitch is a bit gimmicky. Never really heard anyone making use of it in a good track.</p>
          <p><a href="https://disco.auxy.co/t/polyphonic-pitch-bend/3310/21">Read full topic</a></p>
        ]]></description>
