      <item>
        <title>Polyphonic pitch bend</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[blakkaz]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <aside class="quote" data-post="19" data-topic="3310" data-full="true">
<div class="title">
<div class="quote-controls"></div>
<img alt="" width="20" height="20" src="https://sjc6.discourse-cdn.com/standard10/user_avatar/disco.auxy.co/produk/40/3511_1.png" class="avatar"> Produk:</div>
<blockquote>
<p>You can do what he did with the pitch bend in auxy. It’s just bending entire chords.</p>
</blockquote>
</aside>
<p>Nope.</p>
<p>The Seaboard uses MIDI Polyphonic Expression (MPE), which Auxy doesn’t currently support.</p>
